  "instructions": [
    "Rinse rice and cook according to package instructions. Let it cool.",
    "In a large pan or wok, heat olive oil over medium-high heat. Add onion and garlic, sauté for about 3 minutes until fragrant.",
    "Add broccoli florets and stir-fry for another minute. Season with salt, pepper, and the minced chilies if using.",
    "Stir in rum and chicken broth; bring to a simmer. Gradually add coconut milk, stirring constantly to avoid lumps. Simmer for 2 minutes until thickened.",
    "Add cooked rice to the pan, toss gently to combine all ingredients evenly. Serve hot with extra soy sauce or chili oil on the side if desired."
